  "text": "The expression of constitutively active or dominant negative form of HIF-1α in MDA-MB231 cells increases or decreases the metastasis and the blood vessel density in long bones; the HIF-1α knockdown by shRNA reduces the radiographic area of osteolytic lesions, decreases vessel density in bone metastasis, and increases survival time after the injection of breast cancer cells [CITATION_1] .",
